4️⃣ Identity Profile
Kya hai
Identity Profile = Rule / configuration jo decide karta hai ki 
source se aane wale data se Identity kaise create hogi.
Ye decide karta hai:-
kaunsa Source use hoga
kaun-kaun se attributes map honge
identity ka display name kya hoga
lifecycle state kya hogi

Example:-
HR system se data aata hai:

first_name = Rahul
last_name  = Kumar
email      = rahul@company.com
department = IT

Identity Profile mapping:

HR.first_name → Identity.firstName
HR.last_name  → Identity.lastName
HR.email      → Identity.email

Output Identity:-
Name: Rahul Kumar
Email: rahul@company.com
Department: IT

()Identity Profile Important Attributes:-
Attribute	             Kya karta hai
name------------------Identity profile ka naam
source----------------Kaunsa source use hoga
identityAttribute-----Unique identity attribute
displayName-----------User ka display name
accountCorrelation----Accounts ko identity se match karta hai
lifecycleStates-------User lifecycle define karta hai

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
